thread.title: Anne
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Anne

author: Anne
title: Anne
text: Omega collected us at our Queenstown motel (as pre-arranged) and once paperwork was done in their office handed over keys. We wanted a small automatic car for a couple of days and the model was perfect. Dropped it back - with full tank a couple of days later in Queenstown and were taken to the airport. All worked out well and staff efficient.
